0:03 that’s clearly the showdown between Phil and Keanu, and it’s because of them the boat crashes. It’s not Ben because in the leaked photos and footage of Ben and Keanu on the boat Max is wearing the square patterned coat we see him wearing a lot and he’s wrapped up soaking wet while Keanu is bone dye with a bloody, beaten face. So Ben must end up in the water at some point himself. I’ve said all along Phil will be the cause of everything that happens on the boat. And with Sharon the top person to die and Linda in a very close second. He’ll either push one of the women of because of their current situations (Sharon gives birth on the boat and Linda is pissed all the time!) Or he’ll watch as one of them falls overboard Sharon due to blood loss or Linda losses her balance because of all the alcohol and he won’t help them, which would lead into his next storyline. Keanu is gone again permanently by the end of next week if it’s Sharon he’ll end up taking his son with him.
0:05 that’s Ben and Keanu In the water you can tell by their clothes and footwear.
